<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I needed to face the pain,
but the closer I got,</i></font>

953
01:01:28,639 --> 01:01:33,192
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>the only thing I felt
was... dread.</i></font>

954
01:02:05,039 --> 01:02:06,268
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't do this.</font>

955
01:02:11,199 --> 01:02:12,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Bart.</font>

956
01:02:14,800 --> 01:02:16,153
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you hungry?</font>

957
01:02:18,559 --> 01:02:21,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">I, uh... I heard you
come in last night,</font>

958
01:02:21,599 --> 01:02:26,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">so, I made some bacon
and, uh, cinnamon rolls</font>

959
01:02:26,599 --> 01:02:31,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">and... a-a frittata, which I
just learned how to make.</font>

960
01:02:32,599 --> 01:02:34,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">When did you learn how to cook?</font>

961
01:02:34,599 --> 01:02:37,195
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, I been learning
a lot lately.</font>

962
01:02:38,880 --> 01:02:41,793
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why don't you go on in there?
I-I set the table.</font>

963
01:02:44,000 --> 01:02:45,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go on.</font>

964
01:02:48,159 --> 01:02:49,594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here.</font>

965
01:02:56,559 --> 01:03:02,351
<font color="#FFFFFF">The key to the frittata
is how hot you make the pan.</font>

966
01:03:04,519 --> 01:03:05,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's the secret.</font>

967
01:03:11,320 --> 01:03:12,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go on and sit down.</font>

968
01:03:16,239 --> 01:03:18,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take that one.
Yeah, go ahead.</font>

969
01:03:21,960 --> 01:03:23,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">Want some bacon?</font>

970
01:03:29,719 --> 01:03:33,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, uh... wanna say grace?</font>

971
01:03:33,679 --> 01:03:36,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

972
01:03:38,199 --> 01:03:39,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll do it.</font>

973
01:03:42,199 --> 01:03:45,795
<font color="#FFFFFF">God, it's me here, Arthur.</font>

974
01:03:46,480 --> 01:03:51,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wanna thank you
for, uh, answering my prayer.</font>

975
01:03:53,239 --> 01:03:54,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">And, uh...</font>

976
01:03:54,599 --> 01:03:57,976
<font color="#FFFFFF">rub-a-dub-dub,
and thanks for the grub.</font>

977
01:03:58,000 --> 01:03:59,320
<font color="#FFFFFF">Amen.</font>

978
01:04:12,440 --> 01:04:16,815
<font color="#FFFFFF">So you f...
found God or something?</font>

979
01:04:16,840 --> 01:04:20,175
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, I-I been listening
to some preachers on the radio</font>

980
01:04:20,199 --> 01:04:25,150
<font color="#FFFFFF">and, uh, re... uh,
reading the Bible and whatnot.</font>

981
01:04:25,280 --> 01:04:26,335
<font color="#FFFFFF">What part?</font>

982
01:04:26,360 --> 01:04:28,615
<font color="#FFFFFF">All of it.</font>

983
01:04:28,639 --> 01:04:32,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">And, uh, couple of times,
actually.</font>

984
01:04:32,679 --> 01:04:36,215
<font color="#FFFFFF">And, uh, it's pretty confusing.</font>

985
01:04:36,239 --> 01:04:39,438
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's... like <i>Leviticus.</i></font>

986
01:04:41,960 --> 01:04:46,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is that?
I-I-I don't get it.</font>

987
01:04:46,159 --> 01:04:47,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">What prayer?</font>

988
01:04:49,039 --> 01:04:51,695
<font color="#FFFFFF">You said God answered a prayer.
What prayer?</font>

989
01:04:51,719 --> 01:04:54,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just seeing you again.</font>

990
01:04:56,119 --> 01:04:58,735
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, Dad, I been busy.</font>

991
01:04:58,760 --> 01:05:02,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.</font>

992
01:05:02,159 --> 01:05:05,376
<font color="#FFFFFF">I guess you noticed
I've got a few projects</font>

993
01:05:05,400 --> 01:05:06,976
<font color="#FFFFFF">going on around here.</font>

994
01:05:07,000 --> 01:05:09,016
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I got one out in the garage</font>

995
01:05:09,039 --> 01:05:10,856
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was hoping
that you'd help me with.</font>

996
01:05:10,880 --> 01:05:16,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh... I been, uh,
rebuilding that Jeep of mine.</font>

997
01:05:16,480 --> 01:05:19,295
<font color="#FFFFFF">And, man, when I was your age,</font>

998
01:05:19,320 --> 01:05:21,496
<font color="#FFFFFF">I made some memories
in that Jeep.</font>

999
01:05:21,519 --> 01:05:25,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I was hoping
that maybe we could, uh,</font>

1000
01:05:25,800 --> 01:05:29,554
<font color="#FFFFFF">get it running again and...
I don't know...</font>

1001
01:05:31,079 --> 01:05:32,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go somewhere, do some...
What're you doing?</font>

1002
01:05:32,639 --> 01:05:36,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is this?</font>

1003
01:05:39,400 --> 01:05:41,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, I-I-I wrote you
some letters.</font>

1004
01:05:41,599 --> 01:05:42,775
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you get 'em?</font>

1005
01:05:42,800 --> 01:05:45,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. Threw 'em away.</font>

1006
01:05:45,480 --> 01:05:48,135
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you read 'em?</font>

1007
01:05:48,159 --> 01:05:49,389
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Nope.</i></font>

1008
01:05:51,559 --> 01:05:53,391
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh.</font>

1009
01:05:55,320 --> 01:05:57,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">I thought that's why
you came back last night.</font>

1010
01:05:59,840 --> 01:06:02,215
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm... well...</font>

1011
01:06:02,239 --> 01:06:04,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was just trying to make
a memory, that's all.</font>

1012
01:06:04,679 --> 01:06:07,295
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's kind of hard
for me to do, Dad.</font>

1013
01:06:07,320 --> 01:06:10,255
<font color="#FFFFFF">'Cause all the memories
that we have together are bad.</font>

1014
01:06:10,280 --> 01:06:13,590
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh, do you want some...
I'll get some ketchup.</font>

1015
01:06:21,000 --> 01:06:25,856
<font color="#FFFFFF">Son, I-I know that
I-I did some things that...</font>

1016
01:06:25,880 --> 01:06:28,110
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>You did some things?</i></font>

1017
01:06:29,639 --> 01:06:30,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got a memory for you, Dad.</font>

1018
01:06:32,800 --> 01:06:35,295
<font color="#FFFFFF">That night you beat me so badly</font>

1019
01:06:35,320 --> 01:06:38,391
<font color="#FFFFFF">that I had to sleep on my
stomach 'cause I was so bruised?</font>

1020
01:06:39,480 --> 01:06:40,800
<font color="#FFFFFF">I couldn't move.</font>

1021
01:06:42,519 --> 01:06:45,114
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>What was I, ten? 11?</i></font>

1022
01:06:48,480 --> 01:06:50,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah, I remember that.</font>

1023
01:06:52,239 --> 01:06:56,056
<font color="#FFFFFF">That, uh...
that tore me up.</font>

1024
01:06:56,079 --> 01:06:59,436
<font color="#FFFFFF">I-I cried that... all night
about what I did to you then.</font>

1025
01:06:59,559 --> 01:07:01,815
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I cried too, Dad.</i></font>

1026
01:07:01,840 --> 01:07:05,117
<font color="#FFFFFF">In pain all night.</font>

1027
01:07:07,719 --> 01:07:09,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why were you?</font>

1028
01:07:12,840 --> 01:07:15,115
<font color="#FFFFFF">And now you just wanna
come back in here?</font>

1029
01:07:15,239 --> 01:07:16,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">Make breakfast?</font>

1030
01:07:16,679 --> 01:07:17,936
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pretend like nothing
ever happened?</font>

1031
01:07:17,960 --> 01:07:19,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">It doesn't work that way, Dad!</font>

1032
01:07:24,159 --> 01:07:27,755
<font color="#FFFFFF">What am I gonna do, Bart?
I-I just...</font>

1033
01:07:27,880 --> 01:07:31,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wanna make things right
with you and me.</font>

1034
01:07:31,679 --> 01:07:33,114
<font color="#FFFFFF">And, um...</font>

1035
01:07:36,039 --> 01:07:37,335
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I don't know what to say.</i></font>

1036
01:07:37,360 --> 01:07:41,856
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I don't know how to do it.
I'm trying.</i></font>

1037
01:07:41,880 --> 01:07:45,032
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm reading a lot of books
I don't understand, and I'm...</font>

1038
01:07:47,960 --> 01:07:52,096
<font color="#FFFFFF">I just got a lot of questions
about myself.</font>

1039
01:07:52,119 --> 01:07:54,077
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I don't have nobody to...</i></font>

1040
01:07:56,559 --> 01:07:59,233
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>to answer 'em for me.</i></font>

1041
01:08:03,639 --> 01:08:08,735
<font color="#FFFFFF">If God can forgive
everybody else...</font>

1042
01:08:08,760 --> 01:08:10,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">why can't He forgive me?</font>

1043
01:08:18,560 --> 01:08:20,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">God <i>can</i> forgive you.</font>

1044
01:08:23,600 --> 01:08:24,828
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't.</font>

1045
01:08:29,239 --> 01:08:31,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't believe
I came back here.</font>

1046
01:08:31,119 --> 01:08:33,555
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can't you give me a chance?
No!</font>

1047
01:08:35,520 --> 01:08:39,416
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've just gotta give up
on that dream, Dad.</font>

1048
01:08:39,439 --> 01:08:43,672
<font color="#FFFFFF">'Cause it keeps you from this.
From knowing what's real.</font>

1049
01:10:43,560 --> 01:10:45,815
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do it.</font>

1050
01:10:45,840 --> 01:10:47,274
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go ahead.</font>

1051
01:10:49,479 --> 01:10:51,073
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just do it.</font>

1052
01:11:43,319 --> 01:11:45,073
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad, are you dying?</font>

1053
01:11:54,800 --> 01:11:56,074
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.</font>

1054
01:12:06,479 --> 01:12:07,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can show you, Dad.</font>

1055
01:12:11,079 --> 01:12:13,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">With your questions,
I can show you how.</font>

1056
01:12:41,479 --> 01:12:43,775
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>So if you didn't
bring your journals,</i></font>

1057
01:12:43,800 --> 01:12:45,199
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>come up here.</i></font>

1058
01:12:45,319 --> 01:12:47,515
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>You're gonna need them
for your session tonight.</i></font>

1059
01:12:53,279 --> 01:12:56,775
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Tonight we're gonna talk
about forgiveness.</i></font>

1060
01:12:56,800 --> 01:13:00,095
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>So find a blank page in your journal,</i></font>

1061
01:13:00,119 --> 01:13:02,456
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and I want you to write these words...</i></font>

1062
01:13:02,479 --> 01:13:07,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">"God, tonight I choose to forgive,"</font>

1063
01:13:07,720 --> 01:13:09,676
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and I want you to finish that sentence.</i></font>

1064
01:13:10,840 --> 01:13:12,496
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Now, you may say to me,</i></font>

1065
01:13:12,520 --> 01:13:16,615
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>"You don't know how hard it is for me
to forgive this person.</i></font>

1066
01:13:16,640 --> 01:13:19,015
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>You don't know what they've done to me."</i></font>

1067
01:13:19,039 --> 01:13:22,396
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I'd say, "I know it's hard.</font>

1068
01:13:23,840 --> 01:13:26,376
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>But if you have been forgiven by God,</i></font>

1069
01:13:26,399 --> 01:13:28,994
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>then he gives you the power
to forgive others."</i></font>

1070
01:13:58,920 --> 01:14:01,037
<font color="#FFFFFF">Better late than never.</font>

1071
01:14:04,119 --> 01:14:05,997
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll get the door.</font>

1072
01:14:13,199 --> 01:14:16,238
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We got a special treat
for you this morning.</i></font>

1073
01:14:17,840 --> 01:14:21,037
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Any of y'all heard the story
of John Newton?</i></font>

1074
01:14:22,279 --> 01:14:24,935
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>He was a sea captain.</i></font>

1075
01:14:24,960 --> 01:14:26,895
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Slave trader.</i></font>

1076
01:14:26,920 --> 01:14:29,456
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>He was tormented and racked</i></font>

1077
01:14:29,479 --> 01:14:32,576
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>with guilt and shame.</i></font>

1078
01:14:32,600 --> 01:14:34,556
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Well, he found for forgiveness.</i></font>

1079
01:14:35,960 --> 01:14:37,695
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>He found Christ.</i></font>

1080
01:14:37,720 --> 01:14:41,015
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>He wrote a little song about that</i></font>

1081
01:14:41,039 --> 01:14:43,935
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>called "Amazing Grace."</i></font>

1082
01:14:43,960 --> 01:14:46,095
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>That song touched the world.</i></font>

1083
01:14:46,119 --> 01:14:47,975
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey.
<i>What?</i></font>

1084
01:14:48,000 --> 01:14:50,496
<font color="#FFFFFF">I figured out why you like junk.</font>

1085
01:14:50,520 --> 01:14:53,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?
Why you like to fix things.</font>

1086
01:14:53,119 --> 01:14:54,935
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why you...</font>

1087
01:14:54,960 --> 01:14:57,555
<font color="#FFFFFF">you make something
out of nothing all the time.</font>

1088
01:14:58,399 --> 01:15:02,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">They got a word for that.</font>

1089
01:15:02,119 --> 01:15:05,815
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>What's that word?</i>
It's "redemption."</font>

1090
01:15:05,840 --> 01:15:07,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">Redemption.</font>

1091
01:15:07,479 --> 01:15:09,935
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. Hey.</font>

1092
01:15:09,960 --> 01:15:12,296
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is... what is this note here?</font>

1093
01:15:12,319 --> 01:15:14,496
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right there.
What is that note?</font>

1094
01:15:14,520 --> 01:15:16,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">G.
Yeah.</font>

1095
01:15:16,479 --> 01:15:18,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's that note?
C.</font>

1096
01:15:18,680 --> 01:15:20,136
<font color="#FFFFFF">C, all right.
G to C.</font>

1097
01:15:20,159 --> 01:15:22,935
<font color="#FFFFFF">You got some competition now, boy.</font>

1098
01:15:22,960 --> 01:15:25,315
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.
Yeah.</font>

1099
01:15:42,840 --> 01:15:44,319
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Bart Millard!</i></font>

1100
01:15:45,600 --> 01:15:47,751
<font color="#FFFFFF">You gotta hold still, Dad.</font>

1101
01:15:47,880 --> 01:15:50,895
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, sorry.
<i>It's okay.</i></font>

1102
01:15:54,039 --> 01:15:55,855
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Oh, I wanted to be there.</i></font>

1103
01:15:55,880 --> 01:15:58,076
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's all right, Dad.
Ahh.</font>

1104
01:15:59,239 --> 01:16:01,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, there's Shannon.</font>

1105
01:16:03,880 --> 01:16:06,775
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Boy, you better hang onto that girl.</i></font>

1106
01:16:06,800 --> 01:16:09,416
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't you ever let her get away.</font>

1107
01:16:09,439 --> 01:16:11,975
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dad, we're not... we're not dating anymore.</font>

1108
01:16:12,000 --> 01:16:14,895
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>What? What?</i></font>

1109
01:16:14,920 --> 01:16:16,376
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>What'd you do?</i></font>

1110
01:16:16,399 --> 01:16:18,695
<font color="#FFFFFF">You two are meant for each other.</font>

1111
01:16:18,720 --> 01:16:20,951
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Whatever you did,</i></font>

1112
01:16:21,079 --> 01:16:24,198
<font color="#FFFFFF">even if you don't know what you did,
you're wrong.</font>

1113
01:16:26,399 --> 01:16:28,960
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did I ever tell you how I met your mom?</font>

1114
01:16:32,439 --> 01:16:34,296
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell me.</font>

1115
01:16:34,319 --> 01:16:36,895
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Hey, this is Shannon.</i></font>

1116
01:16:36,920 --> 01:16:38,735
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Leave a message.</i></font>

1117
01:16:38,760 --> 01:16:41,296
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Hey, Shannon.</i></font>

1118
01:16:41,319 --> 01:16:43,695
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I don't know if you're getting
these messages or not,</i></font>

1119
01:16:43,720 --> 01:16:47,176
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>but I just wanted you to know
that I'm... I'm back home,</i></font>

1120
01:16:47,199 --> 01:16:50,296
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and I'm... I'm journaling again.</i></font>

1121
01:16:50,319 --> 01:16:54,376
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I'm writing a lot like we did
when we were kids.</i></font>

1122
01:16:54,399 --> 01:16:56,278
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>It feels really good.</i></font>

1123
01:17:58,640 --> 01:18:00,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">I love you, boy.</font>

1124
01:18:17,119 --> 01:18:19,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was listening, Bart.</font>

1125
01:18:21,079 --> 01:18:23,390
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I was listening to you.</i></font>

1126
01:18:25,960 --> 01:18:27,712
<font color="#FFFFFF">On the radio.</font>

1127
01:18:30,359 --> 01:18:33,055
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>'Cause you'd sing...</i></font>

1128
01:18:33,079 --> 01:18:35,615
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and I'd listen to every word.</i></font>

1129
01:18:35,640 --> 01:18:38,296
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And then...</i></font>

1130
01:18:38,319 --> 01:18:39,935
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>you'd finish.</i></font>

1131
01:18:39,960 --> 01:18:44,216
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And then I'd listen to what they were
talking about there at church.</i></font>

1132
01:18:44,239 --> 01:18:46,277
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>That's what saved me.</i></font>

1133
01:18:49,000 --> 01:18:51,560
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I was real proud of you.</i></font>

1134
01:18:54,199 --> 01:18:56,237
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Was real proud.</i></font>

1135
01:18:57,920 --> 01:19:01,515
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I told you not to follow your dreams.</i></font>

1136
01:19:02,880 --> 01:19:05,935
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>But that's only because mine,</i></font>

1137
01:19:05,960 --> 01:19:08,190
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>they never came true.</i></font>

1138
01:19:09,239 --> 01:19:11,197
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>But you're not me.</i></font>

1139
01:19:13,960 --> 01:19:15,837
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're not like me.</font>

1140
01:19:17,920 --> 01:19:19,354
<font color="#FFFFFF">Unh-unh.</font>

1141
01:19:22,239 --> 01:19:24,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">And you, you have a gift.</font>

1142
01:19:26,239 --> 01:19:28,231
<font color="#FFFFFF">A real gift.</font>

1143
01:19:30,159 --> 01:19:32,277
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wanna take care of you, Bart.</font>

1144
01:19:33,279 --> 01:19:36,576
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got something for you, Bart.</font>

